Title: fy_QuickFire
Date of creation: 15 Jul 14
Creators: Stacey B Starr
Target game: CS:S



QUICK DESCRIPTION:

Fast paced, action packed source map designed to keep you on your toes.
IF YOU CAN DOMINATE THIS MAP... YOU CAN DOMINATE ANY MAP!!!!

Each player is spawned in a room with one enemy. Who ever survives the stand off has 

to face the other survivers in the hallway.

Ammo is limited so use your bullets wisely, or atleast save enough to make it to the 

top of the map where there are plenty of weapon pick-ups


ADDITIONAL INFORMATION:

This is our first ever map, we only figured out how to use WWMT for 3DSMAX about 4 

hours ago, and this is our first project to come out of it, so please let us know if 

there is anything that we can improve on.

SPECIAL THANKS:

Just gotta quickly say thanks to 
Source for such an amazing engine.
Autodesk for mind blowing 3d modelling software.
Wall Worm for making such an easy method of exporting maps straight from Max into 

Source games.
Gamebana for being so awesome.
And you for your amazing mouse clicking skills that got you to this download :D
